question: Identify the streams that have the most moderators.
cypher:
MATCH (s:Stream)
OPTIONAL MATCH (s)-[:MODERATOR]->(m:User)
WITH s, count(m) AS moderatorCount
RETURN s.name AS streamName, moderatorCount
ORDER BY moderatorCount DESC
LIMIT 10
review_reason: OPTIONAL MATCH not handled - TypeQL requires moderation relation but should include streams with 0 moderators
